Happy to.

627
00:30:14,417 --> 00:30:16,201
One more word.

628
00:30:18,777 --> 00:30:20,606
You okay?

629
00:30:20,606 --> 00:30:22,764
No.

630
00:30:32,028 --> 00:30:35,643
Today the Saviors
will gather our souls.

631
00:30:35,643 --> 00:30:37,926
All hail
Children of the Stars.

632
00:30:37,926 --> 00:30:40,170
The worthy will ascend
into the heavens.

633
00:30:40,170 --> 00:30:41,250
All hail
Children of the Stars.
Excuse me.

634
00:30:41,250 --> 00:30:42,496
