652
00:31:16,059 --> 00:31:17,886
And yet he's not here.

653
00:31:19,424 --> 00:31:21,542
What's your name?

654
00:31:22,622 --> 00:31:23,786
Aurora.

655
00:31:23,786 --> 00:31:25,115
How old are you, Aurora?

656
00:31:25,115 --> 00:31:28,312
19.

657
00:31:28,312 --> 00:31:29,558
It is
the age of the chosen.

658
00:31:29,558 --> 00:31:31,552
Aren't you scared?

659
00:31:31,552 --> 00:31:32,924
