693
00:33:10,123 --> 00:33:12,158
Can I ask you
a theoretical question?

694
00:33:12,158 --> 00:33:13,737
Sure.

695
00:33:13,737 --> 00:33:16,395
Okay, say, uh,
there's a divorced couple

696
00:33:16,395 --> 00:33:18,390
