702
00:33:30,393 --> 00:33:31,931
Yeah.

703
00:33:31,931 --> 00:33:33,551
Is that bad?

704
00:33:35,295 --> 00:33:37,705
To the court,
it's not good.

705
00:33:37,705 --> 00:33:41,360
