00:39:15,328 --> 00:39:16,950
But when that alert
came in,

811
00:39:16,950 --> 00:39:18,942
the only thing
I could think about

812
00:39:18,942 --> 00:39:20,937
was making sure
that she was safe.

813
00:39:20,937 --> 00:39:23,429
That is the only thing
that matters to me now.

814
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:34,145
Okay.

815
00:39:34,145 --> 00:39:36,888
Okay.

816
00:39:36,888 --> 00:39:38,383
Let's go home.

